### **AI REFACTOR Phase** (25-35 min)

**Rule**: Enhance same AI methods tests call
**Forbidden**: New AI types, files, interfaces
**Validation**: Built-in through REFACTOR phase enhancement focus

**AI-Specific REFACTOR Focus**:
